      "rationale": "Grid convergence index was computed for flow-field quantities (pressure rise, shear stress) across three mesh refinement levels. GCI for the hemolysis index itself was computed only at the 5 L/min reference point; the remaining four operating points lack formal discretization error estimates on the QOI."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
